'''Yemma Xliǧa''', lalla Xliǧa, (s [[Tafrensist|tefrensist]] : sommet de Lalla Khadîdja, s [[taɛrabt]] : قمة لالة خديجة), neɣ '''Tamguṭ''' akken i s-sawalen yimezdaɣ n tudrin i s-d-yezzin, d taqacuct tunnigt deg udrar n [[Ǧerǧer]], tesɛa 2308 m deg teɣzi. Deg beṭṭu adeblan, taqacuct n Yemma Xliǧa tettekki ar tɣiwant n [[Ṣaḥariǧ]] deg [[Tanebḍit n Tubiret|tnebḍit n Tubiret]].
